      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-04352'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040303_GCR_208' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 2 [<span class="italic">Transfer of Property and Staff, etc.</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-04353'>
