      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-04358'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040303_GCR_214' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Andrews</span> moved Amendment No. 63:
        <q>Page 16, line 38, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>9A (1) The Health and Safety at Work (Northern Ireland) Order 1978 (S.1. 1978/1039 (N.I. 9) is amended as follows.</q>
        <q>(2) In Article 18(2) (consultation before approving code of practice). in sub-paragraph (a) for "the National Radiological Protection Board" there is substituted "the Health Protection Agency".</q>
        <q>(3) In Article 46(3) (consultation before submission of proposals for regulations), in sub-paragraph (a) for "the National Radiological Protection Board" there is substituted "the Health Protection Agency".</q>
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_316gc' title='Col. 316GC &mdash; HL Deb 03 March 2004 vol 658 c316GC' name='column_316gc' href='#column_316gc' rel='bookmark'>316GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-04359'>
