        <q>Page 17, line 2, at beginning insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>( ) The <a href="/acts/national-health-service-and-community-care-act-1990">National Health Service and Community Care Act 1990</a> is amended as follows.</q>
        <q>Page 17, line 2, leave out from "4" to end of line.</q>
        <q>Page 17, line 5, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>( ) In section 21(2) (bodies in respect of which schemes may be made for meeting certain losses and liabilities) before "but a scheme under this section" there is inserted the following paragraph&#x2014;</q>
        <q>(d) the Health Protection Agency,".</q>
        <q>Page 17. line 14, leave out "(da)" and insert "(db)</q>
        <q>Page 17, line 16, leave out "(db)" and insert "(dc)</q>
        <q>Page 17, line 23. leave out sub-paragraph (4).</q>
      </p>
      
